data.description: This well maintained West side colonial has everything you need! Beautifully renovated kitchen includes custom cherry cabinets, granite countertops, tiled backsplash and stainless steel appliances. Dining room has great space and is right off the kitchen for all your entertaining needs. The living room runs the length of the house with picture framed walls and a fireplace that brings the whole room together. On the second floor you have a full bath, 3 spacious bedrooms with gleaming hardwood floors, even has a "Beauty Room" for one of the bedrooms. Both bathrooms updated in 2018, newer driveway, fenced in yard, walk up attic, partially finished basement, 3 season porch off main bedroom, Too much to list!
